00:14:38,833 --> 00:14:41,125
- KAORU-SAMA?

314
00:14:41,208 --> 00:14:44,958
ARE YOU GOING TO GO LOOK
FOR MISS TAEKO?

315
00:14:45,041 --> 00:14:46,208
- UH-HUH.

