00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:48,958
- UH, BUT IT'S--

318
00:14:49,041 --> 00:14:50,416
- I BEG OF YOU.

319
00:14:50,500 --> 00:14:53,083
I'M ALSO WORRIED ABOUT 
MISS TAEKO, KAORU-SAMA.

320
00:14:53,166 --> 00:14:55,416
- AOI-CHAN.

321
00:14:55,500 --> 00:14:58,916
- ( wind blowing )

322
00:14:59,000 --> 00:15:01,125
- IT'S PITCH-BLACK.

323
00:15:01,208 --> 00:15:02,416
FOLLOW ME.

324
00:15:02,500 --> 00:15:04,833
AND DON'T EVER LEAVE
MY SIDE, AOI-CHAN, OKAY?

325
00:15:06,916 --> 00:15:08,083
- RIGHT.

326
00:15:08,166 --> 00:15:12,166
MISS TAEKO!
- TAEKO-CHAN!

327
00:15:12,250 --> 00:15:14,166
- MISS TAEKO!

328
00:15:14,250 --> 00:15:16,583
- TAEKO-CHAN!

329
00:15:16,666 --> 00:15:19,375
- ( wood creaking )

330
00:15:21,291 --> 00:15:23,166
- OH.

331
00:15:37,500 --> 00:15:40,208
- THE WIND'S PICKING UP
AND THE FOG TOO.

332
00:15:41,458 --> 00:15:42,833
- ( squawks )

333
00:15:42,916 --> 00:15:44,000
- AAH.

334
00:15:44,083 --> 00:15:45,500
JUST-- JUST A BIRD.

335
00:15:45,583 --> 00:15:48,666
