IF I WAS ALONE.

337
00:15:51,083 --> 00:15:53,833
( chuckles )
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT, AOI-CHAN?

338
00:15:53,916 --> 00:15:55,416
- OH.

339
00:15:55,500 --> 00:15:57,166
I AM PERFECTLY ALL RIGHT.

340
00:15:57,250 --> 00:15:58,875
BUT WE OUGHT TO HURRY.

341
00:15:58,958 --> 00:16:01,541
I'M CERTAIN MISS TAEKO
MUST FEEL OVERWHELMED,

342
00:16:01,625 --> 00:16:03,250
SINCE SHE'S ALL ALONE
RIGHT NOW.

343
00:16:03,333 --> 00:16:05,916
- YE-- YEAH.
THAT'S TRUE.

344
00:16:06,000 --> 00:16:07,791
I'M IMPRESSED.

345
00:16:07,875 --> 00:16:10,375
AOI-CHAN ISN'T SCARED OF
THINGS LIKE THIS?

346
00:16:14,791 --> 00:16:16,000
HERE IT IS.

347
00:16:16,083 --> 00:16:17,333
- WHERE'S MISS TAEKO?

348
00:16:17,416 --> 00:16:19,833
- TAEKO-CHAN!
- MISS TAEKO!

349
00:16:19,916 --> 00:16:21,291
- TAEKO-CHAN!

350
00:16:21,375 --> 00:16:23,875
- WHERE ARE YOU,
MISS TAEKO!

351
00:16:26,041 --> 00:16:27,958
COULD SHE BE
INSIDE THE TEMPLE?

352
00:16:28,041 --> 00:16:29,791
- MAYBE.

353
00:16:35,916 --> 00:16:37,500
SHE'S NOT HERE.

354
00:16:37,583 --> 00:16:39,625
WHERE COULD SHE
HAVE GOTTEN TO?

355
00:16:39,708 --> 00:16:41,833
- UH, KAORU-SAMA?
- HUH?

356
00:16:41,916 --> 00:16:43,291
- L-- LOOK THERE.

357
00:16:43,375 --> 00:16:45,291
- ( whirring )

358
00:16:49,166 --> 00:16:51,500
- IT'S HERE!

359
00:16:51,583 --> 00:16:53,166
- Both: OHH!

360
00:16:57,000 --> 00:16:59,708
- WHAT THE-- IS THAT YOU
OVER THERE, SENPAI?

361
00:16:59,791 --> 00:17:03,541
WHAT ARE YOU DOING
ALL THE WAY OUT HERE?

362
00:17:03,625 --> 00:17:06,416
- ( stammers )
TAEKO-CHAN.

363
00:17:06,500 --> 00:17:09,250
- OHH, SO THAT'S IT.

364
00:17:09,333 --> 00:17:12,458
- BUT IN ANY CASE,
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT, MISS TAEKO?

365
00:17:12,541 --> 00:17:13,958
YOU'RE NOT HURT, ARE YOU?

366
00:17:14,041 --> 00:17:17,416
- NO.  I WAS JUST SO ENGROSSED
IN TAKING PICTURES

367
00:17:17,500 --> 00:17:20,208
THAT I REALLY WASN'T
KEEPING TRACK OF THE TIME.

368
00:17:20,291 --> 00:17:22,916
I DIDN'T EVEN NOTICE
HOW MUCH TIME HAD GONE BY.

369
00:17:23,000 --> 00:17:25,708
- I... SEE.

370
00:17:25,791 --> 00:17:27,625
- I'M REALLY SORRY.

371
00:17:27,708 --> 00:17:30,083
IT LOOKS LIKE I'VE BEEN
CAUSING TROUBLE FOR YOU AGAIN.

372
00:17:30,166 --> 00:17:32,541
- WELL, I'M JUST GLAD
YOU WERE ALL RIGHT.

373
00:17:32,625 --> 00:17:34,666
YOU'RE DONE TAKING
YOUR PICTURES, RIGHT?

374
00:17:34,750 --> 00:17:36,791
LET'S GET BACK TO
THE HOTEL, OKAY? 

375
00:17:36,875 --> 00:17:37,791
- ( all gasp )

376
00:17:39,833 --> 00:17:41,916
- Aoi:
THERE'S SO MUCH FOG.

377
00:17:42,000 --> 00:17:44,250
- ( Kaoru sighs )
 THIS ISN'T GOOD.

378
00:17:44,333 --> 00:17:46,083
WE CAN'T SEE A THING NOW.

379
00:17:46,166 --> 00:17:47,583
- Taeko:
IT'LL BE ALL RIGHT.

380
00:17:47,666 --> 00:17:49,958
IT'S A STRAIGHT PATH
BACK TO THE HOTEL.

381
00:17:50,041 --> 00:17:51,958
- PERHAPS,
BUT I THINK IT'S BEST

382
00:17:52,041 --> 00:17:54,125
IF WE WAIT HERE
FOR THE FOG TO CLEAR.

383
00:17:54,208 --> 00:17:57,291
