00:20:35,416 --> 00:20:36,333
- WHAT'S THAT?

436
00:20:36,416 --> 00:20:38,500
- NOTHING.

437
00:20:38,583 --> 00:20:40,291
IT'S REALLY NOTHING AT ALL.

438
00:20:44,083 --> 00:20:46,500
UM, KAORU-SAMA?

439
00:20:46,583 --> 00:20:50,166
WOULD YOU BE WILLING TO 
TAKE ME SOMEWHERE AGAIN?

440
00:20:50,250 --> 00:20:52,000
- HMM?

441
00:20:52,083 --> 00:20:53,916
- THIS WAS THE FIRST TIME

442
00:20:54,000 --> 00:20:56,750
THAT I WAS EVER ABLE TO
GO ON A FIELD TRIP LIKE THIS.

443
00:20:56,833 --> 00:20:59,750
- SURE.  THE PHOTO CLUB
HAS PLENTY OF OTHER TRIPS

444
00:20:59,833 --> 00:21:01,958
