449
00:21:10,416 --> 00:21:11,708
- LET'S.

450
00:21:11,791 --> 00:21:15,083
- WE'D BETTER GO WAKE
TAEKO-CHAN UP AND GET BACK.

451
00:21:15,166 --> 00:21:17,250
- MISS TINA AND THE OTHERS
MUST BE WAITING.

452
00:21:17,333 --> 00:21:18,916
- WELL, LET'S GO.

453
00:21:22,750 --> 00:21:25,083
- ( door opens )
- SENPAI!

454
00:21:25,166 --> 00:21:26,750
I DID IT!

455
00:21:26,833 --> 00:21:28,416
I GOT A GREAT PICTURE.

456
00:21:28,500 --> 00:21:29,541
LOOK AT ALL THE GHOSTS.

457
00:21:29,625 --> 00:21:31,916
- ( both gasp )
NO WAY!

458
00:21:32,000 --> 00:21:33,416
- IS SOMETHING THE MATTER,
SENPAI?

459
00:21:33,500 --> 00:21:35,583
- WELL, YOU SEE...

460
00:21:35,666 --> 00:21:37,416
IT'S NOT AS GOOD
AS THE ONE WE TOOK,

461
00:21:37,500 --> 00:21:39,583
BUT I'LL ADMIT THAT
YOU GOT THE RIGHT ATTITUDE

462
00:21:39,666 --> 00:21:41,958
TOWARDS PHOTOGRAPHY,
MINAZUKI.

463
00:21:42,041 --> 00:21:43,750
- DEVELOP YOUR TECHNICAL SKILLS

464
00:21:43,833 --> 00:21:46,333
AND YOU'LL BE A PROUD
MEMBER OF THE PHOTO CLUB.

465
00:21:46,416 --> 00:21:47,458
- YES, SIR!

466
00:21:47,541 --> 00:21:49,416
I'LL CONTINUE TO DO
MY VERY BEST!

467
00:21:49,500 --> 00:21:51,166
- ( bell dings )

468
00:21:51,250 --> 00:21:55,125
- ( theme music playing )

469
00:21:55,208 --> 00:21:57,125
- ( singing in Japanese )

470
00:23:20,958 --> 00:23:24,208
- Tina: HEY, MISS LANDLORD,
WHAT'S WHITE AND WARM

471
00:23:24,291 --> 00:23:26,083
