WHAT IS IT?!

472
00:23:26,166 --> 00:23:27,166
- ( doorbell rings )
- Aoi: KAORU-SAMA?

473
00:23:27,250 --> 00:23:28,500
- Tina: HUH?

474
00:23:28,583 --> 00:23:31,083
